tch-on-ISO-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-IP-watch-on-ISO_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-IP-watch-on-ISO_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Saez, Catherine. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ip-watch.org/2012/05/18/international-standards-key-to-helping-the-world-with-many-issues-iso-says/\">\"International Standards Key To Helping The World With Many Issues, ISO Says\"</a>. Intellectual Property Watch<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2 November</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=International+Standards+Key+To+Helping+The+World+With+Many+Issues%2C+ISO+Says&amp;rft.pub=Intellectual+Property+Watch&amp;rft.aulast=Saez&amp;rft.aufirst=Catherine&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ip-watch.org%2F2012%2F05%2F18%2Finternational-standards-key-to-helping-the-world-with-many-issues-iso-says%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AISO+22715\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-ISO-Office-and-Number-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-ISO-Office-and-Number_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">International Organization for Standardization. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.iso.org/iso/iso_technical_committee%3Fcommid%3D54974\">\"ISO/TC 217 Cosmetics\"</a>. ISO.org<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2 November</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=ISO%2FTC+217+Cosmetics&amp;rft.pub=ISO.org&amp;rft.au=International+Organization+for+Standardization&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iso.